      • lex

        public abstract AbstractToken lex(LexicalAnalyzer lexicalAnalyzer)
        Lexes a new AbstractToken with the given LexicalAnalyzer which is used to call methods like LexicalAnalyzer.next(int) or LexicalAnalyzer.peekChar(int).
        Parameters:
        lexicalAnalyzer - the LexicalAnalyzer which should get used for method calls like LexicalAnalyzer.next(int) or LexicalAnalyzer.peekChar(int).
        Returns:
        null if an error occurred or itself/some other token if it lexed successfully.
